 "prompt": "A lone lighthouse on a black tidal rock at dusk, its lamp a small gold smear against a wall of incoming sea-fog; the horizon empty, gulls scattered high. Moody scratchboard linework over salt-bleached ink washes, iron grey and lamp-oil gold against deep tidal green-black. Wide, uncluttered composition with open sky at the top for a title."
